    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A dashboard-style, thematic SPA. The structure guides the user from the "Why" (market shift) to the "How" (WWT's strategy) and the "What" (the V.I.C.E. blueprint and roadmap). This non-linear, thematic structure is chosen over a direct report translation to allow different stakeholders (sales, engineering, leadership) to quickly navigate to sections relevant to them, enhancing usability and comprehension of the complex strategy. Key interactions include tabs for comparison, interactive diagrams for structure, and accordions for detailed recommendations, making dense information digestible. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Report Info: Broadcom Partner Program Changes -> Goal: Compare -> Viz: Interactive Tabs -> Interaction: Click to switch views -> Justification: Simplifies dense table comparison. -> Library/Method: HTML/JS.
        - Report Info: Customer Price Hikes (20-400%) -> Goal: Inform/Show Magnitude -> Viz: Bar Chart -> Interaction: Hover for tooltips -> Justification: Clearly visualizes data range and impact. -> Library/Method: Chart.js (Canvas).
        - Report Info: Knowledge Hub Architecture -> Goal: Explain Structure -> Viz: HTML/CSS Diagram -> Interaction: Hover for details -> Justification: More intuitive than text for hierarchies. -> Library/Method: HTML/Tailwind CSS.
        - Report Info: Key Recommendations -> Goal: Organize/Inform -> Viz: Accordion -> Interaction: Click to expand -> Justification: Manages content density and focuses user attention. -> Library/Method: HTML/JS.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
