                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 flex-grow">For clients remaining with VMware, we provide unparalleled support. We help them navigate licensing changes, optimize costs, and leverage their investment, particularly with VCF as a foundation for their AI and hybrid cloud strategies.</p>
